summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessement and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6292 for the improvement of Blake Place Southwest and Vashon Place Southwest each from the Southwest Othello St. to Southwest Fontanelle St.; and a certain other street and avenue; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 92390 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
